1.0.0 BETA PREVIEW - March 26, 2008
===================================
- Added arp-convert.php utility script to import data from AutoRank Pro 5.0.x (March 25, 2008)
- Added arphp-convert.php utility script to import data from AutoRank PHP 3.0.x (March 25, 2008)
- Added the {featured} ranking page template function to display a featured site (March 26, 2008)
- Added the storecatranks attribute for the {accounts} ranking page template function (March 26, 2008)
- Added fields to store each account's rank from the last build in the database (March 26, 2008)
- Fixed issue with search generating an error message when no categories were defined (March 26, 2008)
- Added display of referring URL stats in the control panel account stats interface (March 26, 2008)



1.0.0 BETA PREVIEW - March 18, 2008
===================================
- End user search function completed (March 12, 2008)
- Default template set updated for a consistent look between all pages (March 12, 2008)
- Added URL encoding function (March 12, 2008)
- Added ability to automatically remove uncofirmed accounts through cron (March 13, 2008)
- Added the image.php script to display ranking images on member sites (March 13, 2008)
- Added storeranks attribute for the {accounts} ranking page template function (March 13, 2008)
- Added the secret key value for direct link (embedded) tracking mode (March 17, 2008)
- Added ability to send surfer to a random site with the out.php script (March 17, 2008)
- Added ability for end users to view the surfer comments submitted for a site (March 17, 2008)
- Added ability for end users to rate and submit comments for sites (March 18, 2008)
- Added quick tasks interface for Search Accounts (March 18, 2008)



